  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening the Arabic Language in UNESCO - year 3</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Language is perhaps the most distinctive and defining feature of any human society. It is pivotal in the realm of information technology, the tool that all modern sectors use, and the foundation on which modern human communication is established. 
With the aim to enhance multilinguism, and address the many-faceted relations between Arabic and the system of knowledge acquisition, a set of activities will be implemented in the following categories: Publications /Translation of existing material ; Activities/initiatives to promote the Arabic Language; Production and dissemination of Knowledge in Arabic; Web and Media; Interpretation in Arabic</narrative>
  </description>
